<div id="header">

<p>
<h2>The most important part of a bug's life is triage.</h2>
</p>
</div>

<div id="content">

<p>
Sorting, filtering and analyzing our incoming bugs every day helps Mozilla find problems 
sooner and ship great software to hundreds of millions of users. 
</p>

<p>
If you can give us a few minutes of your day, you can help Mozilla move faster. 
We'll send you an email with links to new issues our community is facing, and we'd
like your help sorting them into the right components and asking the right questions,
so they can get to the right people with the right information. 
</p>

<p>Sign up here:
</p>

<p>
<form action="index.py" method="post">
<div class="form"><div class="label">Name or IRC handle:</div> <div class="choice"><input type="text" name="nickname"/></div></div>
<div class="form"><div class="label">Email address:</div><div class="choice"><input type="text" name="email" /></div></div>
<div class="form"><div class="label">Number of bugs:</div>
<div class="choice"><select name="number">
<option value="1">1</option>
<option value="2">2</option>
<option value="3">3</option>
<option value="5">5</option>
<option value="8">8</option>
<option value="12">12</option>
<option value="15">15</option>
</select></div></div>
<div class="form"><div class="label">How often?</div> 
<div class="choice"><select name="rate">
<option value="daily">Daily</option>
<option value="workdays">Mon-Fri</option>
<option value="weekly">Weekly</option>
</select></div></div>
<div class="form"><div class="label">&nbsp;</div><div class="choice"><input type="submit" value="Submit"></div></div></p>
</form>
</p>
</div>
</div>

